I go around to the front and this dog ya know has a bunch of flies on him and me being a caring person was trying to pet him and get some flies off him. Next thing i know he jumps up and bites me in the face, course i run home crying my eyes out. I ended up going to the hospital and getting a load of stitches in my mouth around the upper lip area. The dog was put down sadly (learned after the fact his previous owner flicked him in the balls when he did something wrong). Sad day for both me and the dog
